%define name @PACKAGE_TARNAME@

Name: @PACKAGE_TARNAME@
Summary: General include files and C++ functions.
Group: Utilities
Version: @VERSION@
Release: @RELEASE@
License: GPL
#BuildHost: %{_hostname}

Source: @PACKAGE_TARNAME@-@VERSION@.tar.gz
URL: git://agander/@PACKAGE_TARNAME@.git

BuildRoot: %{_tmppath}/%{name}-root
Prefix: %{_prefix}

Provides: %{name} = %{version}-%{release}

%description
Various program:
- length: output the length oa string;
- buildCtags: Create/update the vim ctags file from all include/ directories;
- create_autoconf_skeleton: Create a autoconf/cmake project suitable for KDevelop.
- dbgoutput.hpp: Provides a functiod for displaying messages during development.
- general.hpp: strtolong<>(): Template functiod to convert strings to long.

%prep
%setup

%build
